:"Norfolk, England, United Kingdom","Great Massingham, Norfolk, Eng.":"Great Massingham, Norfolk, England, United Kingdom","nameMeanings":[{"name":"Felton","type":"LAST","attribution":"Dictionary of American Family Names © Patrick Hanks 2003, 2006.","meanings":["English: habitational name from any of various places so called. Most of them, including those in Herefordshire, Shropshire, and Somerset (Winford), are named from Old English <i>feld</i> ‘pasture, open country’ + <i>tūn</i> ‘enclosure, settlement’. Another place of the same name in Somerset, also known as Whitchurch, has as its first element Old English <i>filethe</i> ‘hay’. Felton Hill in Northumberland is named with the Old English personal name <i>Fygla</i> (a derivative of <i>fugol</i> ‘bird’; compare   Fowle  )."],"variants":[{"name":"Fowle","meanings":["English (Kent): patronymic from the Middle English personal name <i>Foghel</i>, <i>Fughel</i> (Old English <i>Fugel</i>, <i>Fugol</i>, from Old English <i>fugol</i> ‘fowl, bird’). Alternatively, a nickname from Middle English <i>fughel</i>, <i>foghel</i>, <i>foul</i> ‘fowl, bird’, either with reference to physical appearance, size, or behavior, or possibly also a nickname for someone who kept or sold birds.","Americanized form of German   Faul  ."]}]},{"name":"Muriel","type":"FIRST","attribution":"Dictionary of First Names © Patrick Hanks and Flavia Hodges 1990, 2003, 2006.","meanings":["Of Celtic origin (  see  Muireall   ). Forms of the name are found in Breton as well as in Irish and Scottish Gaelic, and in the form   Meriel   it was in use in the heart of England in the Middle Ages. The surname <i>Merrill</i> is derived from it. As <i>Muriel</i> it was at first used mainly in Scotland, but became more widely popular during the first half of the 20th century. Since then it has fallen from favour again."],"variants":[]}],"lifeSummary":"Muriel Felton was born about 1245. She married Bertram WODEHOUSE in 1259, in Great Massingham, Norfolk, England. They were the parents of at least 1 son."},"et":{"about 1245–":"umbes 1245–Surnud","1245–Male":"1245–Surnud","1240–1548":"1240–1548","1273–Male":"1273–Surnud","1274–Male":"1274–Surnud","1276–Male":"1276–Surnud","1278–Male":"1278–Surnud","1260–1320":"1260–1320","1245–Female":"1245–Surnud","Abt 1259":"umbes 1259","1274":"1274","abt. 1276":"umbes 1276","1273":"1273","1240":"1240","1260":"1260","Abt 1273":"umbes 1273","1259":"1259","1278":"1278","1245":"1245","1320":"1320","1276":"1276","about 1245":"umbes 1245","about 1278":"umbes 1278","1548":"1548","Kimberley Manor, Norfolk, England":"Kimberley, Norfolk, England","Great Massingham, Norfolk, England":"Great Massingham, Norfolk, Inglismaa, United Kingdom","Norfolk, England":"Norfolk, Inglismaa, United Kingdom","Great Massingham, Norfolk, Eng.":"Great Massingham, Norfolk, Inglismaa, United Kingdom"},"fi":{"about 1245–":"noin 1245–Kuollut","1245–Male":"1245–Kuollut","1240–1548":"1240–1548","1273–Male":"1273–Kuollut","1274–Male":"1274–Kuollut","1276–Male":"1276–Kuollut","1278–Male":"1278–Kuollut","1260–1320":"1260–1320","1245–Female":"1245–Kuollut","Abt 1259":"noin 1259","1274":"1274","abt. 1276":"noin 1276","1273":"1273","1240":"1240","1260":"1260","Abt 1273":"noin 1273","1259":"1259","1278":"1278","1245":"1245","1320":"1320","1276":"1276","about 1245":"noin 1245","about 1278":"noin 1278","1548":"1548","Kimberley Manor, Norfolk, England":"Kimberley, Norfolk, England","Great Massingham, Norfolk, England":"Great Massingham, Norfolk, Englanti, Yhdistynyt kuningaskunta","Norfolk, England":"Norfolk, Englanti, Yhdistynyt kuningaskunta","Great Massingham, Norfolk, Eng.":"Great Massingham, Norfolk, Englanti, Yhdistynyt kuningaskunta"},"fr":{"about 1245–":"environ 1245–Décédée","1245–Male":"1245–Décédé","1240–1548":"1240–1548","1273–Male":"1273–Décédé","1274–Male":"1274–Décédé","1276–Male":"1276–Décédé","1278–Male":"1278–Décédé","1260–1320":"1260–1320","1245–Female":"1245–Décédée","Abt 1259":"environ 1259","1274":"1274","abt. 1276":